{"tid":1141712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到完場]鄭家純 對 新垣結衣 2018-19 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強次回合","createTime":"2019-05-06T16:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T14:04:46.000Z","uid":92376,"like":60,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41ad9b152e129e17e84cc4f8230c0433f3ee991b","tid":1141712,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鄭家純 v 新垣結衣<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強次回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-5-7 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UsZqZk4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUsZqZk4.png&h=d24896af&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/U0qLaqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FU0qLaqX.png&h=76eb16f3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/c4H073L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc4H073L.png&h=24615d99&s={SIZE}\" />鄭家純 v 新垣結衣<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=cf9c1fd7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" />ili.cheng #aragakiyui<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合 38-133)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能(前正後負)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"8345d87fbb3f5c3751064f5087a2dd12aaed95df","tid":1141712,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"雞排領先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85c736f276f6ab1142dfcd38f30fbe8e03a969a","tid":1141712,"uid":135959,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"傻撚咗牙投雞扒妹？？？"},{"pid":"07d6015071764dfd41e36317553400e3d1f2917d","tid":1141712,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d85c736f276f6ab1142dfcd38f30fbe8e03a969a","tid":1141712,"uid":135959,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"傻撚咗牙投雞扒妹？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"啲人見佢可憐掛<br />\n因為總比數結衣已經領先百幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267ff0b23813cbdc73c12068b973a50c1a0fdf2d","tid":1141712,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07d6015071764dfd41e36317553400e3d1f2917d","tid":1141712,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d85c736f276f6ab1142dfcd38f30fbe8e03a969a","tid":1141712,"uid":135959,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"傻撚咗牙投雞扒妹？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"啲人見佢可憐掛<br />\n因為總比數結衣已經領先百幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"90幾分"},{"pid":"0c5b3fbb8588769b203c7440d8a93ff24f8703e2","tid":1141712,"uid":164166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05